message.body: I am. Here till 4. Hanging with my friend Emily after. You on Biggie duty this weekend?
Ah, thought you were doing a Biggie sit. Leaving for Asheville on Monday to spread my mom's ashes. I'll be back next weekend and we can make a plan to hang.
Ok I that sounds good. I'll be just hanging out near south street between 6 and 10 tonight if you wana meet up. Otherwise we can do something next week
Ok, sounds good. With Emily now and having dinner with friends later. Let's plan on getting together when I get back from Asheville.
